text: Aliksei Uladzimiravich Mzhachyk (; 30 June 1996 â€“ 1 August 2021) was a Belarusian weightlifter. He came in 12th place in the men's +105 kg event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. He was born in Pinsk, Belarus. Mzhachyk was killed in a car crash on 1 August 2021 in Germany, aged 25. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Olympians for Belarus Category:Weightlifters Category:Road accident deaths
